to the F.B.I.

14
00:00:50,017 --> 00:00:53,986
Mail a duplicate copy
to the Sundance Film Festival.

15
00:00:53,988 --> 00:00:56,922
Okay? Make sure
you attach a note.
Tell 'em it's a rough cut.

16
00:00:56,924 --> 00:00:58,757
You know, still working
on some things.
But mostly it's all there.

17
00:00:58,759 --> 00:01:00,392
Just gotta put
the title sequence in,
it'll be all set.

18
